title: World2_Friend_Explain
position: 74,-243
---
<<set_right friend_surprised>>
<<highlight right>>

<<if $friend_route == 1>>
    Friend: Ah... So you know. I was going to tell you eventually.
<<else>>
    Friend: Ah... So you know. Your reactions are better than I expected.
<<endif>>

<<set_right friend_neutral>>
Friend: There is too much to lose. Hundreds of people live here. Their happiness depends on that child. And so it is important that we look away — for the sake of the many.

<<highlight left>>
-> Yes, that does make sense.
    <<set_left mc_smiling>>
    <<set $friend_agreed = true>>
    <<jump World2_Friend_Close>>
-> I am still not so sure about that.
    <<set_left mc_neutral>>
    <<set $friend_agreed = false>>
    <<jump World2_Friend_Close>>
-> No way.
    <<set_left mc_neutral>>
    <<set $friend_agreed = false>>
    <<jump World2_Friend_Pushback>>
===

title: World2_Friend_Pushback
position: -105,5
