<<highlight right>>
Friend: Don't do something foolish you will regret. This is not what I invited you here for.
Friend: I have invited you here, so you can have a look at difference in people's perspectives.

<<jump World2_Friend_Close>>
===

title: World2_Friend_Close
position: 52,274
